    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. some of my more skeptical students might ask if this isn't just a way for judges to make up their own laws instead of actually following the text of the Constitution. how should I explain the legitimacy of using this doctrine compared to just sticking to the literal words of the Constitution?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
